## GPT-5.6 - official SoT

OpenAI: [Prompting guidance for GPT-5.6 Sol](https://developers.openai.com/api/docs/guides/prompt-guidance-gpt-5p6)

Aligned with our kit:

| OpenAI | Orchestra use |
|--------|----------------|
| Outcome + constraints + evidence + completion bar | Goal + Success + Stop |
| Lean prompts (drop repeated process) | Never paste full AGENTS into worker |
| Autonomy / approval boundaries | stamp, G1, write locks |
| Effort / verbosity = API | pin in Orca command, not prose |
| Check work before finish | Success validation + EXEC-REPORT |

**Algorithm:** every dispatch runs `references/dispatch-algorithm.md` (role → family → shape → pin → send → identity gate).

Terra / Sol / Luna are product variants of the same family - still use **Goal + Success + Stop**.
